CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1952, pg. 17, reads: "Nutrition Class At Hill City - Members of this Red Cross Nutrition and Food Cost Class are shown at Hill City. Mrs. Eunice Cook, far left, seated, is sponsor of the course.  The study for Hill District housewives is just one of the many services of the Red Cross in Hill District. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Ten women, including Eunice Cook, seated in front row, far left, gathered in Hill City for Red Cross Nutrition and Food Cost Class
